  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393690/extras/6a2f1742c02a87c35a5e8f91287077b8.avif?t=1738173578\" width=630 height=210 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHAT IS TASKS FOR TWO?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab a nearby partner! You've got work to do! <strong><i>Tasks for Two</i></strong> is a cute 2-player local co-op game where you work together to complete a series of tasks. You only have a few seconds to get each one done, so speed and cooperation are key. Complete as many tasks as you can without messing up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393690/extras/e4180cfe49d95ca241eba723c2637111.poster.avif?t=1738173578\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393690/extras/e4180cfe49d95ca241eba723c2637111.webm?t=1738173578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393690/extras/e4180cfe49d95ca241eba723c2637111.mp4?t=1738173578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393690/extras/8284a9020bf229a82bdbe42f352a0273.poster.avif?t=1738173578\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393690/extras/8284a9020bf229a82bdbe42f352a0273.webm?t=1738173578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393690/extras/8284a9020bf229a82bdbe42f352a0273.mp4?t=1738173578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393690/extras/65d114694c7f7213aa8ebe0d0af2751d.poster.avif?t=1738173578\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393690/extras/65d114694c7f7213aa8ebe0d0af2751d.webm?t=1738173578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393690/extras/65d114694c7f7213aa8ebe0d0af2751d.mp4?t=1738173578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CREDITS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nick Donnoli - </strong>Creator, programmer, composer, and illustrator</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sarah Lam -</strong> Illustrator (Bird, Bunny, and logo) </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FLASHING IMAGE WARNING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game contains flickering images and patterns that may trigger seizures in those with photosensitive epilepsy. If you are prone to this, please do not play this game (or any other game for that matter). Thank you, and stay safe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393690/extras/6a2f1742c02a87c35a5e8f91287077b8.avif?t=1738173578\" width=630 height=210 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHAT IS TASKS FOR TWO?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab a nearby partner! You've got work to do! <strong><i>Tasks for Two</i></strong> is a cute 2-player local co-op game where you work together to complete a series of tasks. You only have a few seconds to get each one done, so speed and cooperation are key. Complete as many tasks as you can without messing up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393690/extras/e4180cfe49d95ca241eba723c2637111.poster.avif?t=1738173578\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393690/extras/e4180cfe49d95ca241eba723c2637111.webm?t=1738173578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393690/extras/e4180cfe49d95ca241eba723c2637111.mp4?t=1738173578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393690/extras/8284a9020bf229a82bdbe42f352a0273.poster.avif?t=1738173578\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393690/extras/8284a9020bf229a82bdbe42f352a0273.webm?t=1738173578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3393690/extras/8284a9020bf229a82bdbe42f352a0273.mp4?t=1738173578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span cla